Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The space city Side 3 proclaimed itself\Nthe Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,During this war, the Principality of Zeon\Nand the Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...caused the deaths of\Nhalf the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Icelina - Love's Remains
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...deep in outer space,\Nat the furthest distance from Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...float dozens of space cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Principality of Zeon,\Na space city-state ruled by the Zabi family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...who seek to impose their dictatorship\Nupon all of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Within these giant cylindrical structures\Nfloating in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...there is a world in which people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,These cylinders are\Napproximately 6 km in diameter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...and over 30 km in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An artificial living environment\Nhas been created within...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people are able to live\Nas though they were on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the commander of\NZeon's Space Attack Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...Vice Admiral Dozle Zabi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...has just returned\Nfrom his frontline base.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's changed in six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No new fortifications have been built.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Space cities use centrifugal force\Nto generate gravity, and as a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...people live along the inner wall\Nof the cylindrical capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Z um City, the capital\Nof the Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot let Garma's death be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The honor of the Zabi family is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gihren, I just want Garma's death to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse my interruption.\NLord Dozle Zabi and Lady Kycilia Zabi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...have presently arrived from the frontlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You two made it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! You must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It is regrettable that Garma should fall\Nbefore the Federation's mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother, I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep thinking he'll show up any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't win any battles\Nby dwelling on the past, Dozle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was looking forward\Nto him becoming a general...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...who'd be giving me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as Dozle says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, Gihren...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...we must pray for the peaceful repose\Nof Garma's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...in a quiet and respectful manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Miss Icelina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Icelina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching you from a distance\Nat that last party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...all the officers present were praising\Nyour beauty and grace, Miss Icelina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the room that was\Nused by Lord Garma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This must surely be a time\Nof great sorrow for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But we will not let them go unpunished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Icelina, we will absolutely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lieutenant Darota...\N- Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me aboard the Gaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Icelina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The vile enemy who killed my Garma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The least I can do\Nis exact revenge upon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But... that would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Darota...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a bit early for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come this far. We're as good as there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that the Federation Forces\Nare coming to pick us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're impatient! It'll be first-come,\Nfirst-served as soon as we land!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We've hit some powerful turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe an air pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have hit turbulence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll get rough for a while, but don't worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did you figure it out?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The built-in safety valve prevented it\Nfrom extending into the javelin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! It looks like you're\Npretty well-suited for engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you use both as javelins?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! They're both the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enemy aircraft sighted at 11 o'clock!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser analysis... They're Gaws!\NThree Gaws approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished with the Gundam maintenance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, we can launch anytime!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The engines aren't performing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright. How about an emergency landing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just a stone's throw away\Nfrom reaching Federation airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rescuers could be on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Bright, the White Base shoulde.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get caught in the turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, It'll help me dodge a direct hit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro, we're going to jump to that spot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...I'll try!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming! Fire on the mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile suits!\NThey're responsible for Garma's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We will avenge Captain Garma's death\Nno matter what, Miss Icelina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire! Shoot them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu! It's more powerful\Nbecause we're so close to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to destroy the gun turrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 2, cover Number 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,l-Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any fighter planes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, after the last few battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...the number of combat-ready planes is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Char. I'll give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lt. Commander Char, It's me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lieutenant Darota, formerly under{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who you are.\NAim for the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cockpit, sir?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The belly. It's the heart of the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I will attack the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to finish them off for good now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taking responsibility for Garma's death...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Showing loyaltyDozle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Either way, I can't lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A message from the Federation Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The liaison conference at General HQ\Nis still in deadlock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we can't expect reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, even Matilda's Medea helping us\Nhas become an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they care what happens to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more to the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Preparing to take on refugees."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Head for point S-109, N-23."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mirai! Change course, 1.5 degrees!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy aircraft at 10 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The safety's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been hit! Port-side rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! I can't switch over the power!\NWe've lost control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency landing!\NHang on to something, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Buckle your seat belts if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Landing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be an easy way\Nto capture the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai. You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't due to my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to the White Base's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Ms. Sayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:14:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Could you please go check on the refugees?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, for the most part!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's drop down to the ground for a while!\N- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And please make sure you destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency repairs to the power section are\Ncomplete, so we should be able to manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Power section, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. Power output Is down 25%{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All okay over here. No problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base sure is\Namazingly well-built.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Now we just have to\Nget out of here, fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're hit, we won't be able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I contact Amuro and Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we received any emergency signals?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't caught any signs\Nof malfunctions yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright! Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Several of the refugees have\Nleft the ship without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we can't stand this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting off here is too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Return now! It's not safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy may be near!\NYou have to come back, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zeons are after the White Base\Nand the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We're only in danger\Nbecause we're on the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do in a desert like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with mourning Garma\Njust within our royal family?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, we're at war right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to strengthen\Nthe fighting spirit of our people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...there can be nothing more\Nappropriate than a state funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma's death does not concern him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It concerns the entire Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with Gihren.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, we must deal with Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishing the one who failed\Nto protect Garma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...will serve as an example to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can deal with that\Non your own authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The important thing is\Nthe funeral ceremony, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma was very popular among the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a state funeral for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...will help stir up the people's hatred\Ntoward the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be a vital thing to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as Char is concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...Dozle, have him demoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As sovereign of the Principality of Zeon,\Nplease make your decision now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cover me, Mr. Ryu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Concentrate all fire on the mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't falter! Shoot down the mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My shield's giving way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Hayato! All right, Gaw...\NHere I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Darota!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My arm! I can't pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll take over!\N- Miss Icelina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be fair to Garma\Nif we didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still coming at us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,l-It's still coming at us...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile suit! I will avenge Garma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! One of the circuits was damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! Are you all right?! Amuro?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright, the Gundam is malfunctioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go inspect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right. There may be soldiers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Darota!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Vengeance for Garma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did... Did she say vengeance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Me...? Vengeance on me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you can't rely on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dren. We'll report that my mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...wasn't working because\Nthe electrical systems were all burned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're rescued!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what her name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she wanted vengeance on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro is exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But a new enemy, Ramba Ral,\Ndescends upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The massive destructive power\Nof a new enemy mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...easily overwhelms the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the cry of "Sieg Zeon!" is heard by all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam.\NNext episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Threat of Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Threat of Zeon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:54.74,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:59.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:09.96,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:14.89,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:19.52,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.52,0:24:24.90,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.90,0:24:29.48,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.48,0:24:39.79,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:54.74,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:59.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:09.96,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:14.89,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:19.52,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.52,0:24:24.90,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.90,0:24:29.48,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.48,0:24:39.79,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
